	<section class="article-content clearfix" itemprop="articleBody">
				
		<p>Volunteer needed for Easter Show stand</p>
<p>Youngyaa is an event company aiming to enhance cultural communication between China and Australia. We will have a booth at Sydney Royal Easter Show from 17<sup><span style="font-size: small;">th</span></sup> to 30<sup><span style="font-size: small;">th</span></sup> of March at Olympic Park. The main function of the booth is to promote traditional Chinese culture. Currently, the company is looking for volunteers who would be able to work as our helpers during that period of time.</p>
<p>Requirements:</p>
<ol>
<li>Fluent Mandarin and English is crucial, especially in oral English as majority of the visitors would be Native English speakers.</li>
<li>Previous volunteering experience is highly regarded.</li>
<li>Good interpersonal skills and welcoming manners.</li>
<li>Positive &ldquo;can do&rdquo; attitude and organizational skills</li>
<li>Initiative and enthusiasm</li>
</ol>
<p>Benefits:</p>
<ol>
<li>Free Royal Easter Show Entrance pass</li>
<li>Great opportunity to meet new friends and improve communication skill</li>
<li>Free T- shirt</li>
<li>Free lunch</li>
</ol>
<p>Please send your resume to <span id="cloak61630">This email address is being protected from spambots. You need JavaScript enabled to view it.</span><script type='text/javascript'>
